Further routines in GFA-BASIC 3.X: Load the  graphics-sizes IMG,PAC,PIC,
NEO,PI3,PI2,PI1 and PC3. The  real(ly) routines are in Assembler
written and from there very fast. For all screen resolutions.
As well a GDOS-introduction with VDI-Library, FSM-GDOS will(_be) supports\ed.
